snippet.title: Bioshock Infinite Walkthrough - Part 06: Monument Island
snippet.description:
Full walkthrough playlist: http://bit.ly/YBm8k5

Part 06 of IGN's walkthrough of Bioshock Infinite.

Having made it to Monument Island, Booker now has to make his way inside and up to the top of the statue, where he must rescue Elizabeth and escape her captor, the giant mechanical Songbird.
